{"tid":635101,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有啲野好想知，但諗到自己死果時都得唔到答案就覺得係人生遺憾？","createTime":"2018-04-20T00:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T15:44:35.000Z","uid":8647,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b2b3d371689dd990985996bfb8be15085cb7c8f2","tid":635101,"uid":8647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T00:30:25.000Z","msg":"例如海底最深處除左海棉寶寶其實係有啲咩野？<br />\n<br />\n又例如人要有一個空間（地球）先存在到，地球存在係太陽系，太陽系存在係銀河系等等如此類推，咁諗既話宇宙又存在係咩野入面？<br />\n<br />\n愈諗得多呢啲個人就愈SAD，因為到死果刻我都唔知個答案係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ce4e2beb0286c737d5d8f89fb3bb1e065df3f0","tid":635101,"uid":8647,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T00:30:43.000Z","msg":"Sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"eb4a9faf8948b052f50b1191f92bfb0d9bb0d11e","tid":635101,"uid":14866,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T00:33:45.000Z","msg":"好想知例如一千年後，地球無爆的話人類既科技可以去到咩地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35150ad6d7c66d29bb2622bbd69d5a01ec10d25e","tid":635101,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T00:36:44.000Z","msg":"好想知咩動物一出世就識叫爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac0e4f16a981630da106064bef0fa7fa6d49bc4","tid":635101,"uid":28865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb4a9faf8948b052f50b1191f92bfb0d9bb0d11e","tid":635101,"uid":14866,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T00:33:45.000Z","msg":"好想知例如一千年後，地球無爆的話人類既科技可以去到咩地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T00:40:46.000Z","msg":"ready player one"},{"pid":"90dc3d9d3d29d658521d70d6147abc17a429c0d6","tid":635101,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T00:41:35.000Z","msg":"訓醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de6f6bb882218ea75aa8fd8e27ffa91aeb34c